02:50:07.320 --> 02:50:08.987
Ah, nature!

1713
02:50:09.530 --> 02:50:12.866
Dawn always makes me so emotional.

1714
02:50:13.868 --> 02:50:18.246
I looked so good all made up,
but now I feel sticky.


1715
02:50:18.497 --> 02:50:22.751
But what do I care?
I'm quitting anyway.


1716
02:50:47.443 --> 02:50:51.112
But the more people retire,
the more others appear.


1717
02:50:53.282 --> 02:50:56.076
If two quit,
ten fill their places.


1718
02:50:56.619 --> 02:51:00.497
By 1965 there'll be total depravity.

1719
02:51:00.831 --> 02:51:04.042
How squalid everything will be!

1720
02:51:05.461 --> 02:51:07.879
Get back!

1721
02:51:14.011 --> 02:51:16.971
You'll make a fortune.
It's worth millions!


1722
02:51:17.723 --> 02:51:19.974
Guys, it's a monster!

1723
02:51:32.113 --> 02:51:34.072
My God!

1724
02:51:36.784 --> 02:51:38.493
It's alive!

1725
02:51:38.661 --> 02:51:40.787
It's been dead for two days.

1726
02:51:44.625 --> 02:51:47.752
- Is it male or female?
- What's it looking at?


1727
02:51:56.011 --> 02:51:57.971
Why don't we buy it?

1728
02:52:03.436 --> 02:52:07.772
Where did it come from?
Maybe Australia.


1729
02:52:07.940 --> 02:52:09.274
Why Australia?

1730
02:52:09.442 --> 02:52:11.776
You can't even tell
the front from the back.


1731
02:52:11.944 --> 02:52:13.903
Poor thing.

1732
02:52:17.533 --> 02:52:19.451
It just keeps staring.

1733
02:53:05.289 --> 02:53:07.749
I don't understand.
I can't hear you.


1734
02:53:28.896 --> 02:53:31.314
I can't hear you.

1735
02:53:39.824 --> 02:53:43.243
- Marcello, come on.
- I'm coming.